{
  "texts": [
    "• Shortage of professionals poses a tremendous barrier to the adoption of AI in the agriculture sector.",
    "Agricultural communities often lack people with expertise in agricultural AI, which poses a barrier to developing, implementing, and maintaining AI systems.",
    "Likewise, deprivation of adequate training and capacity building programs along with non-AIfocused courses leave potential users without opportunities to equip themselves with essential knowledge.",
    "Language barriers and lack of local technical experts in AI makes it difficult to customize AI systems as per local needs.",
    "However, these challenges could be addressed in a number of ways including skill development and knowledge dissemination."
  ]
}